text: The Liberal Party of Australia (Tasmanian Division), commonly called the Tasmanian Liberals, is the Tasmanian branch of the Liberal Party, a centre- right, liberal conservative political party in Australia. It currently forms the state's Government. Its current leader is Jeremy Rockliff (who is the current state Premier) and the deputy leader is Michael Ferguson.
